tgt: Turn left and then walk past the recliner, continue until you turn slightly right, then continue before turning a sharp right and into the room then stop.

src: walk across living room into kitchen
tgt: Walk across living room to hallway into kitchen.

src: stairs turn down stairs turn steps wait there
